{
  "stem": "2833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they had put at night all kind of packages up in the trees with food and stuff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So we got that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then one of the gendarmes whom we befriended-- and he was willing to go to Prague and the other town, to Brunn, which also had girls with us in that group-- and he went and brought us cigarettes, which was more than gold in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You could get a lot more for that than-- money didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he brought us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he brought all kind of news, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was marvelous for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were really very lucky, because the Czech gendarmes were totally on our side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, they had to be very careful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But still, they helped us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Czech forester was a nice man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we just worked during the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we cooked at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had one of those-- we lived in a-- in a former little restaurant with two rooms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each had a coal stove.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got coal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we cooked, and we baked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we ate a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when we went back to Terezin after two months, I think we looked too well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The SS man who was the-- the head of the SS in Terezin at the station, yelled and screamed-- that those fat Jewish sows-- as he called us-- look at them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- we looked too good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
